1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:09,800
Have you contacted Lu San?

2
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:13,200
It's fine.

3
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:15,800
Lao San is smart.

4
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:20,000
I'm afraid Lao Er won't make it this time.

5
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:23,300
If the police question him, what if he...

6
00:00:26,640 --> 00:00:27,370
Don't worry.

7
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:29,640
Lao Er has never let me down.

8
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:32,240
But Ah San,

9
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:36,520
I've always protected him since childhood.

10
00:00:36,800 --> 00:00:38,480
He's a bit soft inside.

11
00:00:41,600 --> 00:00:42,880
But it's fine.

12
00:00:44,200 --> 00:00:46,840
No matter what, I'll follow you.

13
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,600
Where are we going now?

14
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:54,320
Guixi.

15
00:00:55,680 --> 00:00:57,160
If Lao San can escape,

16
00:00:58,280 --> 00:00:59,810
he'll know where to find us.

17
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:16,000
Two cases, two dead, one injured,

18
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,600
nearly 100,000 in property.

19
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,039
If you did this alone,

20
00:01:19,039 --> 00:01:20,640
it's enough for two death sentences.

21
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,370
But an accessory is different.

22
00:01:22,640 --> 00:01:24,320
You are still so young.

23
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:26,000
Why ruin your whole life?

24
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:28,200
Then just shoot me,

25
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,800
let me reincarnate early,

26
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:32,000
and be a good person in the next life.

27
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:41,300
Wu Zhaoxiang still refuses to say anything.

28
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:44,640
We didn't catch Hua Weihong or Cao Aiyuan.

29
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:47,320
And Wu Zhaoxiang won't say anything.

30
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,039
I'm so useless.

31
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,440
How are you useless?

32
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:53,330
You risked your life trying to catch Hua Weihong.

33
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,050
I admire you. Here's a toast to you.

34
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,520
I'll toast to you too.

35
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,400
Was I risking my life?

36
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,360
It's just that they value their own lives

37
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,440
more than mine.

38
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,880
Is that how you got your second-class merit?

39
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:18,960
Lao Ma.

40
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,579
Do you know my brother's name?

41
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:24,520
Lin Jian.

42
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,600
You remember now?

43
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:34,160
The cop who was killed by a homemade gun

44
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:36,620
five years ago catching child traffickers.

45
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,260
Actually, I hated it so much then.

46
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:44,200
Why couldn't they investigate the case more carefully?

47
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:46,920
Why couldn't they find that homemade gun?

48
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,400
Isn't it obvious?

49
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,450
I only have one goal.

50
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,120
To inherit my brother's badge number

51
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,980
and become him.

52
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,650
Better than him.

53
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,200
Good.

54
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,180
What's wrong with you?

55
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,120
What do you mean?

56
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,520
Where is Yinuo's mom?

57
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:09,480
Stop asking.

58
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,720
What do you mean stop asking?

59
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,120
I've already poured my heart out.

60
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,640
I told you not to ask, so don't.

61
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,240
Why should I listen to you?

62
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:17,040
Alright, stop arguing.

63
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,980
There's nothing I can't be asked.

64
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,200
It's the first time we've had such a good talk.

65
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,320
Let's talk more.

66
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:28,320
These are words from the bottom of my heart.

67
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,240
Ready. One, two, three.

68
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,360
Ta-da!

69
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,320
Take a look.

70
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,040
How is it?

71
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,000
The team assigned me this new apartment.

72
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,320
Look, I bought all this furniture myself.

73
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:40,980
This will be our marital home.

74
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,360
Do you like it?

75
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:45,320
What's the point of a nice apartment?

76
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,560
You are so busy with work.

77
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,960
Won't I still be alone after we get married?

78
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,000
You always put work first.

79
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:53,200
How can you even talk about having kids?

80
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,760
Come on, don't say that.

81
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,800
I just got promoted to vice-captain.

82
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,000
It's normal to be busy.

83
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,460
It means the team needs me.

84
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,640
Anyway, I'll focus on work first.

85
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:04,880
Let's talk about having kids in a couple of years, okay?

86
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:15,520
Who is she?

87
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,610
She is my sister.

88
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,680
You are already a senior, you know?

89
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,880
You have to take the graduate entrance exam next year.

90
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,120
This is the most critical time.

91
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,320
It concerns your future.

92
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,780
Now that you're pregnant,

93
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,040
what will you do in the future?

94
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,160
Didn't he say he would take responsibility for you?

95
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:30,960
Where is he?

96
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,720
He said he had to go out to do something,

97
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:36,200
and he'll come back and marry me once he makes money.

98
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:38,400
I want to wait for him at home for a while.

99
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,440
Xiaoying.

100
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,290
Where are you going?

101
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,330
I'm leaving.

102
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,180
This is my brother.

103
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:52,490
He is the father of my child.

104
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:53,760
Brother.

105
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,330
His name is Li Qiang.

106
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,760
You don't need to worry about me.

107
00:04:57,760 --> 00:04:58,720
Take a look.

108
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:02,020
Ma, a notice just came from above.

109
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,640
This wanted criminal has come to Guangnan.

110
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:05,650
Investigate it.

111
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,980
Isn't he coming back to pick me up?

112
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,440
Did you tell him

113
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,760
what your brother does?

114
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,400
Our brother is a cop.

115
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:24,600
Xiaoying and I have a train to catch.

116
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,120
We are leaving now.

117
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,440
Go.

118
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:26,970
Alright.

119
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,370
We're off, brother.

120
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:31,840
Stop.

121
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,600
Don't leave.

122
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,930
Come to the police station with me.

123
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:47,040
I saw your wanted poster today. Drug trafficking.

124
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,520
You can't escape.

125
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:52,400
Brother, I really didn't traffic drugs.

126
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,120
Brother, please believe me.

127
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,000
After that day,

128
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,760
my sister never spoke a word to me again.

129
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:08,400
She gave Yinuo to me after she was born,

130
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,560
and never appeared again.

131
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,520
During this time,

132
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:22,560
My fiancée also left me.

133
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,960
Since Yinuo was born,

134
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:28,200
I brought her up little by little.

135
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,320
So Yinuo and I are the closest.

136
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:34,720
But as she grew older and more sensible,

137
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:36,800
she became introverted,

138
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,180
and even somewhat withdrawn.

139
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,000
Except with me,

140
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,330
she didn't interact much with outsiders.

141
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,770
But the children are innocent!

142
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,560
Including Nuannuan, she is innocent too.

143
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,920
Li Na and Chen Zhaodi, they are innocent as well.

144
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,780
They were murdered for no reason.

145
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:55,580
These beasts did such filthy things.

146
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,280
They must be caught and shot.

147
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,600
If only there were no criminals.

148
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,160
Is that possible?

149
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,920
I wish there weren't any either.

150
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,920
Then my brother wouldn't have died.

151
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:11,480
So our duty as police officers is

152
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:14,560
to bring all criminals to justice.

153
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,720
Alright, bring them to justice.

154
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,650
Bring them to justice. Come on!

155
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,320
Master.

156
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,680
Your cooking smells as good as ever.

157
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:44,520
Hua.

158
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,820
Come here quickly.

159
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,450
Have another bite, Master.

160
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,880
Hurry, hurry, hurry.

161
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,250
Let's go.

162
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:01,720
Honey.

163
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:04,200
You're letting someone stay at our house again?

164
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,280
Today this one stays here,

165
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,520
and tomorrow that one stays here.

166
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,480
Do you think our house is a hotel?

167
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:10,000
Keep it down. How many times have I told you?

168
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,680
This kid is very close to me.

169
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,400
I usually listen to you on everything.

170
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,660
Listen to me this time.

171
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,400
Come on, hurry up and cook a couple of dishes to go with the drinks.

172
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,660
Let's have a good chat.

173
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:21,860
Master.

174
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,800
Master.

175
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,560
When did this happen?

176
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,680
After you guys left,

177
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,159
I was all alone.

178
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,760
When people get older,

179
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,280
they fear loneliness.

180
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:39,210
Later I met your new master's wife.

181
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,860
She's from the next village and is a nice person.

182
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,600
She just loves to nag.

183
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:48,440
Nagging is good.

184
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:49,840
You just fear having no one to nag you.

185
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,560
Yes, now that you have a companion,

186
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,920
San'er and I are both relieved.

187
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,650
That's good.

188
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,880
How are those two brats?

189
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,760
They are doing well in business.

190
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,480
Good to be busy.

191
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,880
It's good to be busy.

192
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,560
Is this girl your girlfriend?

193
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:08,360
Hello, sir.

194
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,680
Hello.

195
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:13,520
Let me tell you, I can see she has a great personality.

196
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,000
Girl, let me tell you.

197
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,920
These three

198
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,800
have been troublemakers since they were kids.

199
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,600
They were famous on this street.

200
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,400
They'd eat for free wherever they went.

201
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:26,200
Stop talking, sir.

202
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,480
Last time they came here,

203
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,000
they ate and ran.

204
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,040
I was young then,

205
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,360
fast on my feet,

206
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:32,690
so I chased them.

207
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:36,360
San was slow, so I caught him.

208
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,560
Guess what?

209
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:40,280
He stood in front of Lu San.

210
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:41,320
Guess what he said to me?

211
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,600
If you want to beat someone, beat me.

212
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,480
Remember?

213
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:47,880
Hua has been loyal and responsible since childhood.

214
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:50,000
Sir, did you beat him up in the end?

215
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,720
How could I bring myself to do it?

216
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,360
The three of them

217
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,800
are poor kids.

218
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:59,480
They grew up with no parents and no place to live.

219
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:03,520
So I let them stay in my shop and help out.

220
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,410
At least they had a place to stay

221
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:06,600
and food to eat.

222
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:10,000
Well, seeing them all have their own careers now,

223
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,960
I'm relieved.

224
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,080
Let me tell you, Hua.

225
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,680
You found such a good girl.

226
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,160
Live a good life together,

227
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:16,960
you hear me?

228
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,450
Don't make me worry.

229
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:19,820
I'll listen to you.

230
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:20,480
Come on.

231
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:22,960
Huazi.

232
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,410
Now that you're back, don't leave.

233
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,520
Honey, hurry up.

234
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:37,080
Everyone is waiting for you.

235
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,480
Go help Master's wife.

236
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:39,880
Hurry up.

237
00:10:42,160 --> 00:10:43,600
Master, I'll go check on your wife.

238
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,600
No need, no need.

239
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,820
Let her learn. It's fine, Master.

240
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:47,480
Let's drink, Master.

241
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:47,920
Okay.

242
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:48,450
Alright.

243
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:49,000
Come.

244
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:51,760
Ma'am.

245
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:53,160
It's too smoky in the kitchen.

246
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:54,360
Go out and take a seat.

247
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:57,080
It's our first time meeting,

248
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,480
and we didn't prepare much.

249
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,680
Please accept this.

250
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,920
It's a small token of our appreciation.

251
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:03,920
I shouldn't accept this.

252
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,380
It's fine, just accept it.

253
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:08,680
No wonder my Chen kept talking about his apprentice Huazi.

254
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:11,080
He found such a sensible and beautiful wife,

255
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,480
he's really promising.

256
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,520
Ma'am, where are your aprons?

257
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:15,880
I'll help you out.

258
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:18,250
It's in the back, grab it yourself.

259
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,840
This is too much.
